From wettenhall at wehi.EDU.AU  Sun Oct 16 05:27:41 2005
From: wettenhall at wehi.EDU.AU (James Wettenhall)
Date: Sun, 16 Oct 2005 13:27:41 +1000 (EST)
Subject: [R-gui] R GUI considerations (was: R, Wine,
